                            <comment id="12884005" author="rquast" created="Wed, 30 Jun 2010 18:15:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The other files work fine from the original fix, but this attached file still has inverted color problem.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13041194" author="lehmi" created="Mon, 30 May 2011 16:41:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The pdf uses an indexed colorspace and pdfbox didn&apos;t extract the base colorspace to calculate the correct parameter needed for creating the colormodel.&lt;br/&gt;
I fixed this issue in revision 1129244.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13042555" author="rquast" created="Thu, 2 Jun 2011 01:26:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Can confirm that this bug fixed worked for me too. Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13268915" author="kryton" created="Sat, 5 May 2012 07:27:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi guys.&lt;br/&gt;
I&apos;m still seeing this happening.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;but I am using the &apos;write2file()&apos; function on PDXObjectImage to output it. I&apos;ll try to attach the PDF which demonstrates the bug.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13268918" author="kryton" created="Sat, 5 May 2012 07:31:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I can&apos;t attach to this jira. I put the PDF file here - &lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/open?id=0B8poAdcNcdTwZjlwcF9ja0hkSzQ&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://docs.google.com/open?id=0B8poAdcNcdTwZjlwcF9ja0hkSzQ&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
hopefully google hasn&apos;t munged it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13274225" author="lehmi" created="Sun, 13 May 2012 07:38:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;@Ian&lt;br/&gt;
Please don&apos;t hijack already closed issue. On one hand already closed issue won&apos;t get much attention as the are already closed and on the other hand we shouldn&apos;t reopen it as your issue is not directly related to this one (this one is about converting pdfs to images and yours about extracting images of a pdf).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Create a new issue and attach the pdf in question to it. Feel free to ask for help if you still can&apos;t attach it to the issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
